 	in crtc-tmpl.c resp. pet/crtc.c

	* c610/crtc.h (CRTC_WINDOW_TITLE): removed def that shadowed define
        in crtc-tmpl.c resp. pet/crtc.c

	* cia-tmpl.c (read_mycia): when reading CIA_CRA and CIA_CRB
	call update_mycia() to update bit 0 (stopped/running)

